        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series can be shown to diverge by limit comparison with <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the sum, from n equals 1, to infinity, of, the fraction 1 over n\"><math alttext=\"the sum, from n equals 1, to infinity, of, the fraction 1 over n\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munderover><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mrow></math></span></span>.</p>",
